  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="DEMO_MODE">
  <data key="d0">DEMO_MODE</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">DEMO_MODE is a setting that, when enabled, forces the system into a mode where no real LLM calls are made.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d8787c2876f2fa9c466edf1494e57b95</data>
  <data key="d4">49b9b405-a2df-4704-a521-79269f380e63</data>
  <data key="d5">1773847784</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="EMBEDDING_MODEL">
  <data key="d0">EMBEDDING_MODEL</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">EMBEDDING_MODEL refers to the text embedding model used in the system, set to "text-embedding-3-small".</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d8787c2876f2fa9c466edf1494e57b95</data>
  <data key="d4">49b9b405-a2df-4704-a521-79269f380e63</data>
  <data key="d5">1773847786</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="ANTHROPIC_MODEL">
  <data key="d0">ANTHROPIC_MODEL</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">ANTHROPIC_MODEL refers to the model provided by Anthropic used in the system, set to "claude-sonnet-4-6".</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d8787c2876f2fa9c466edf1494e57b95</data>
  <data key="d4">49b9b405-a2df-4704-a521-79269f380e63</data>
  <data key="d5">1773847787</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="OPENAI_MODEL">
  <data key="d0">OPENAI_MODEL</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">OPENAI_MODEL refers to the OpenAI model used in the system, set to "gpt-4o".</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d8787c2876f2fa9c466edf1494e57b95</data>
  <data key="d4">49b9b405-a2df-4704-a521-79269f380e63</data>
  <data key="d5">1773847788</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="COST_LIMIT_USD">
  <data key="d0">COST_LIMIT_USD</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">COST_LIMIT_USD refers to the cost guard setting that blocks pipeline runs estimated over a specified USD amount, set to "0.0" indicating no limit.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d8787c2876f2fa9c466edf1494e57b95</data>
  <data key="d4">49b9b405-a2df-4704-a521-79269f380e63</data>
  <data key="d5">1773847794</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="HTTP Endpoints">
  <data key="d0">HTTP Endpoints</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">HTTP Endpoints refer to URLs exposed by the API for various operations, such as health checks and queries.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d8787c2876f2fa9c466edf1494e57b95</data>
  <data key="d4">49b9b405-a2df-4704-a521-79269f380e63</data>
  <data key="d5">1773847794</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Pipeline SSE">
  <data key="d0">Pipeline SSE</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Pipeline SSE describes the Server-Sent Events functionality in the pipeline run process within the system.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d8787c2876f2fa9c466edf1494e57b95</data>
  <data key="d4">49b9b405-a2df-4704-a521-79269f380e63</data>
  <data key="d5">1773847794</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cost Tracking">
  <data key="d0">Cost Tracking</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Cost tracking refers to the monitoring of costs related to embedding and generation using OpenAI and Anthropic services, and the logging of these costs.&lt;SEP&gt;Cost Tracking refers to the method of tracking embedding and generation costs within the system.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d8787c2876f2fa9c466edf1494e57b95&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b2357e61536898e16b9f8b1b5949ab3</data>
